    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>LEAD:  ''It sort of settled down to just trading arms for hostages, and that's a little like paying ransom to a kidnapper. If you do it, then the kidnapper's just encouraged to go kidnap someone else.''  - President Reagan.  [ A12:3. ]</p>
